# ---------------------------------------------------------------- #
# MONOREPO ROOT — DOCKER BUILD CONTEXT IGNORE
# Applied when build context is the monorepo root (API and Web builds).
# Excludes anything that should not enter the Docker build context.
# ---------------------------------------------------------------- #

# Version control
.git
.gitignore

# Dependencies (rebuilt inside the image)
**/node_modules

# Build artifacts (rebuilt inside the image)
**/dist
**/build
**/.turbo
**/*.tsbuildinfo

# Secrets — NEVER copy env files into a Docker image
**/.env
**/.env.*

# Logs
**/*.log
**/logs

# Test and coverage
**/coverage
**/__tests__
**/*.test.ts
**/*.spec.ts

# Editor and OS artifacts
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Documentation
README.md
CHANGELOG.md
LICENSE.md
